# Responsive Features Section â€“ Frontend UI

A clean, responsive **Features Section UI** built using **HTML5, CSS3, and Bootstrap 4**.  
This project demonstrates strong fundamentals in **responsive layout design**, **Bootstrap grid architecture**, and **readable UI composition**, suitable for modern web interfaces.



