## ğŸ’¼ Why This Project Matters (For Recruiters)

This project showcases:

- Correct usage of **Bootstrap grid system**
- Mobile-first responsive design
- Clean, semantic HTML structure
- Practical CSS for text wrapping and alignment
- Attention to layout constraints and readability
- Ability to debug and fix common Bootstrap mistakes



## ğŸ› ï¸ Tech Stack

- **HTML5**
- **CSS3**
- **Bootstrap 4.5**
- **Google Fonts (Roboto)**
- **Responsive Design Principles**



## ğŸ§© Layout & Responsiveness

| Screen Size | Layout |
|------------|--------|
| Mobile | 1 feature per row |
| Tablet | 2â€“3 features per row |
| Desktop | 3 features per row |

Implemented using:
```html
<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-12 col-md-4">...</div>
  </div>
</div>


## ğŸ¨ UI & Styling Decisions

* Icons constrained for visual consistency
* Headings emphasize hierarchy
* Paragraph width limited for readability
* Automatic word wrapping prevents overflow

```css
.paragraph {
  max-width: 300px;
  margin: auto;
  overflow-wrap: break-word;
}




