## ğŸ“š Key Learnings

* Bootstrap columns must be direct children of `.row`
* Avoid mixing fixed widths with responsive grids
* Text wrapping is controlled by container width, not `<br>`
* Clean structure prevents unpredictable UI bugs
* Readability is a design feature, not an afterthought


## ğŸ”§ Possible Enhancements

* Upgrade to Bootstrap 5
* Convert inline styles to reusable CSS classes
* Add hover states and transitions
* Convert to reusable React component
* Add accessibility improvements (ARIA, contrast)


